msgid "# Set-ClusterStorageSpacesDirectDisk"
msgstr "# 设置集群存储空间（直接使用磁盘）"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid ""
"Configures the system to enable S2D to claim or not claim specific physical "
"disks."
msgstr "配置系统以决定S2D是否可以申请或放弃特定的物理磁盘。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法（Syntax）"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 说明"

msgid ""
"The `Set-ClusterStorageSpacesDirectDisk` cmdlet configures the system to enable Storage Spaces\n"
"Direct (S2D) to claim or not claim specific physical disks. Disks marked to be not claimed by S2D\n"
"remain untouched so that they can be used for other purposes."
msgstr ""
"`Set-ClusterStorageSpacesDirectDisk` cmdlet 用于配置系统，以决定是否允许 Storage Spaces "
"Direct (S2D) 占用特定的物理磁盘。被标记为不被 S2D 占用的磁盘将保持原状，可以继续用于其他用途。"

msgid ""
"To avoid possible clean up and warnings, we recommend that you run this cmdlet before you enable\n"
"S2D. Alternatively, you can run this cmdlet after you enable S2D."
msgstr ""
"为了避免可能出现的清理操作和警告，我们建议您在启用 S2D 之前运行此 cmdlet。或者，您也可以在启用 S2D 之后再运行此 cmdlet。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1: Configure disks not to be claimed"
msgstr "### 示例 1：配置磁盘以防止被占用"

msgid ""
"This command configures the system that physical disks that have the IDs `55CD2E404B75A3FC` and\n"
"`50014EE05950DD7C` cannot be claimed by S2D. In this example, the **CanBeClaimed** parameter is\n"
"explicitly specified as `$False`. Omitting that parameter indicates that the specified physical disks can be claimed."
msgstr ""
"此命令配置系统，使得ID为 `55CD2E404B75A3FC` 和 `50014EE05950DD7C` "
"的物理磁盘不能被S2D程序占用。在这个示例中，**CanBeClaimed** 参数被明确设置为 "
"`$False`；如果省略该参数，则表示指定的物理磁盘可以被S2D程序占用。"

msgid ""
"This example uses splatting to pass parameter values from the `$Parameters` variable to the command.\n"
"Learn more about [Splatting](/powershell/module/microsoft.powershell.core/about/about_splatting)."
msgstr ""
"这个示例使用了“拆分（splatting）”技术，将 `$Parameters` 变量中的参数值传递给命令。有关 [拆分（Splatting）] "
"的更多信息，请参阅 "
"[这里](/powershell/module/microsoft.powershell.core/about/about_splatting)。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid ""
"Runs the cmdlet as a background job. Use this parameter to run commands that take a long time to\n"
"complete."
msgstr "将此cmdlet作为后台作业运行。使用此参数来执行需要较长时间才能完成的命令。"

msgid ""
"The cmdlet immediately returns an object that represents the job and then displays the command\n"
"prompt. You can continue to work in the session while the job completes. To manage the job, use the\n"
"`*-Job` cmdlets. To get the job results, use the\n"
"[Receive-Job](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113372) cmdlet."
msgstr ""
"该 cmdlet 会立即返回一个表示该作业的对象，然后显示命令提示符。在作业完成之前，您可以继续在当前会话中工作。要管理该作业，请使用 `*-Job` "
"系列 cmdlets；要获取作业结果，请使用 [Receive-"
"Job](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113372) cmdlet。"

msgid ""
"For more information about Windows PowerShell background jobs, see\n"
"[about_Jobs](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113251)."
msgstr ""
"有关 Windows PowerShell 后台作业的更多信息，请参阅 [关于作业（About "
"Jobs）](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113251)。"

msgid ""
"Indicates that S2D can claim the physical disks specified by the **PhysicalDiskIds** parameter. If\n"
"you don't specify this parameter, this cmdlet indicates that the specified physical disks can be\n"
"claimed."
msgstr ""
"这表示 S2D 可以获取由 **PhysicalDiskIds** 参数指定的物理磁盘。如果您没有指定此参数，该 cmdlet "
"表示可以获取所指定的物理磁盘。"

msgid ""
"Runs the cmdlet in a remote session or on a remote computer. Enter a computer name or a session\n"
"object, such as the output of a [New-CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227967)\n"
"or [Get-CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227966) cmdlet. The default is the\n"
"current session on the local computer."
msgstr ""
"在远程会话或远程计算机上运行该cmdlet。可以输入一个计算机名称，或者是一个会话对象（例如通过[New-"
"CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227967)或[Get-"
"CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227966) "
"cmdlet获得的会话对象）。默认情况下，该cmdlet会在本地计算机的当前会话中执行。"

msgid "Prompts you for confirmation before running the cmdlet."
msgstr "在运行 cmdlet 之前会提示您进行确认。"

msgid ""
"Specifies an array of unique IDs of physical disks. This cmdlet set S2D to claim or not claim the\n"
"specified disks."
msgstr "指定一个包含物理磁盘唯一ID的数组。该cmdlet用于设置S2D是否要占用这些指定的磁盘。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the maximum number of concurrent operations that can be established to run the cmdlet. If\n"
"this parameter is omitted or a value of `0` is entered, then Windows PowerShell calculates an\n"
"optimum throttle limit for the cmdlet based on the number of CIM cmdlets that are running on the\n"
"computer. The throttle limit applies only to the current cmdlet, not to the session or to the\n"
"computer."
msgstr ""
"该参数用于指定可以同时执行的操作的最大数量。如果省略此参数或输入值为 `0`，则 Windows PowerShell 会根据计算机上正在运行的 CIM"
" cmdlet 的数量来计算该 cmdlet 的最佳限制值。此限制仅适用于当前正在执行的 cmdlet，而不适用于整个会话或计算机本身。"

msgid "Shows what would happen if the cmdlet runs. The cmdlet isn't run."
msgstr "展示了如果运行该cmdlet会发生什么情况。但实际上并没有运行该cmdlet。"

